User Stories for Team 33


As a player I need to log into the game so I can play.
As a database I need to store the players log in name so their name can be attached to their story and score at a later date.
As a player I need to roll dice to generate three images so I can start my turn.
As a player I need to enter text to tell a story corresponding to images so other player can score my story.
As a database I need to store the players story so other players can score it.
As a player I need score other player story so the next player's turn can begin.

